{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- maybe it was 1936, and somebody threw a bomb into that store, and he was killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- so that was one of the first incidents, sort of a terrorist incident.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then other things happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were constant provocations, and-- so yes, it was all around us at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you lived with it and you still had hope that-- that Schuschnigg, who came in, who was a-- a Catholic government.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I forgot now what they called the party, the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] social-- I forgot now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it was Catholic-- basically a Catholic party, which-- which had-- which ran the government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he was conservative, and-- and there was some hope that he would be able to maintain some kind of democracy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But when Hitler became stronger and stronger, it became very ominous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the threats, there with these constants threats of invasion and what he would do and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then you saw Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So yes, we were surrounded by it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The newspapers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were outlawed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Nazi party was outlawed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when they put enormous pressure on Schuschnigg, the last chancellor, then he legalized them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, they-- they were in a position of power, and that was the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in maybe '37, the end of '37.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know, it was-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a constant-- you know, I had never always talked about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was constant turmoil, and-- and-- and-- and I don't have the dates correct, but maybe it was 1933.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Until then, it was a social, democratic government, a socialist-- basically a socialist government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were communists, and there was some Nazis underground, but it was basically a socialist government.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
